metadata.name: Deserted
metadata.description:
We're Lonely  
Stranded  
Surrounded  
Yet Abandoned  
Trusting  
It's Your Arms  
Where We've Landed  
Maybe Our Time  
Maybe It's Commanded  
Reborn  
Washed A New  
Thus Unbranded

a man  
drifting  
not one to follow  
guide of day men to night  
an oracle of apollo  
truths of reality  
i guide  
you swallow

Take Us To Your Darkness  
Give Substance  
To This Pain  
We Feel Hollow

i feel no more  
awake today  
gone tomorrow  
a guide with no direction  
telling stories from no perspective  
yet  
you follow with no incentive  
a path that's purely inventive

Those Bound  
Now Unbound

gather 'round  
the weak  
the bitter  
the meek  
the unique  
the lustful  
the distrustful  
those poor in health  
ill guide  
to those treasures  
i cannot seek myself
